\b\i\fs24 * Description *     \par
\b0\i0\fs20\par
The first mission of my six-mission campaign, which takes place during one night in the town of Rocksbourg.  \par
In this mission, explore Rocksbourg and soak up the atmopshere !\par
\par
These events take place immediately after Thief II and some time before Thief III.\par
\par
This is my first fan mission.  It took quite a lot of trouble to create, and there still might be a bug or two, \par
but I hope the mission is playable.\par
\par
Enjoy!\par
\par
